Estate land with C-of-O in Abuja goes for N1.5m, as T Pumpy announces 40% slash, rewards agents with 10% With 22 housing estate units at Airport Road Abuja, Abuja’s leading real estate developer, T Pumpy Concept has flagged off a December Discount sales that offer prospective homeowners opportunities to purchase a plot of land for the sum of N1.5m instead of the market value N2.5m at its Kuje estate, giving them a huge 40 per cent discount. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857652 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/06062ab7-ea7c-4ee0-937e-d5e47b31d991.jpg" alt="" width="1008" height="756" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/06062ab7-ea7c-4ee0-937e-d5e47b31d991.jpg 1008w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/06062ab7-ea7c-4ee0-937e-d5e47b31d991-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 1008px) 100vw, 1008px"> Besides the slash in price, buyers are given 50kg bag of rice throughout December and for agents who broker the transaction, the enterprising and real estate firm is offering them 10% agency fee, instead of the conventional 5 per cent. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857659 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/05eee1be581e42-tpumpy-estate-mixed-use-land-for-sale-lugbe-district-abuja.jpg" alt="" width="750" height="421" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/05eee1be581e42-tpumpy-estate-mixed-use-land-for-sale-lugbe-district-abuja.jpg 750w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/05eee1be581e42-tpumpy-estate-mixed-use-land-for-sale-lugbe-district-abuja-300x168.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px">  This promo is a continuation of the firm’s slash-in-price property offer aimed at ameliorating the economic effects of Covid-19. The company has given a Honda Crosstour to her best agent last year. The move to increase agents with 10% is to give back to the society and assist government in bridging the unemployment gap as government alone cannot do it. This move would create more jobs for our youths. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857654 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2019-05-16-at-12.13.26.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="375" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2019-05-16-at-12.13.26.jpeg 500w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2019-05-16-at-12.13.26-300x225.jpeg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"> As part of its December Discount promo, the real estate developer is also offering for sale plot of land in its T Pumpy Kiddies Estate. According to AkintayoAdaralegbe, the MD/CEO of the company: “With N399, 000, your child is a landowner with certificate of occupancy. For the said amount, the child gets a 600 square metre land, upon which can be built a three-bedroom bungalow, four-bedroom penthouse or even four or five-bedroom duplex.” <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857655 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82d0e15d-3860-4627-9de9-b8f77b594c38.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="877" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82d0e15d-3860-4627-9de9-b8f77b594c38.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82d0e15d-3860-4627-9de9-b8f77b594c38-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> He further reiterated T Pumpy’s commitment to ensuring that “every man’s dream to own a house is actualized.” While T Pumpy Concept LTD has 22 housing estates spread across Kyami, Kasana, Kuje, Lugbe, Gwagwalada and other places in the nation’s capital, the ongoing December Discount promo is exclusive to its Lugbe estates along the Airport Road. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857656 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5cf7762d3c599.jpg" alt="" width="506" height="462" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5cf7762d3c599.jpg 506w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5cf7762d3c599-300x274.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px"> Pumpy Concept LTD, a registered company that deals in the sales of lands and estate plots since 2009, has over the past ten years built a reputation as an industry-acclaimed off-site home design and construction. T. Pumpy Concept Limited is a progressive property developer that prides itself on its proven track records, passion and commitment to deliver superior value in design, quality and services in our developments to our customers. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857657 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82e1bb13-9d92-4193-a6a5-40d8ad35f495.jpg" alt="" width="987" height="822" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82e1bb13-9d92-4193-a6a5-40d8ad35f495.jpg 987w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/82e1bb13-9d92-4193-a6a5-40d8ad35f495-300x250.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px"> T. Pumpy Concept is a registered company that deals majorly in the sales of lands and estate plots. The company has been in existence since 2009, and it’s totally committed to making its utmost contribution in the development process of our environment in the aforementioned area, for the betterment of all Nigerians. The T-Pumpy Concept team has decades of providing industry-acclaimed off-site home design and construction. Whether you’re interested in a manufactured home or an innovative modular design, the T-Pumpy Concept team continues to deliver what home buyers are looking for in their new homes along with the quality construction they expect and deserve. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857658 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/e52d564c-24c8-415e-a081-6c8c4907ffdc.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/e52d564c-24c8-415e-a081-6c8c4907ffdc.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-cont